title: Real.Housewives.of.Melbourne.s01e09.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description:
Ready to move on with her life, Gina enlists the help of an exclusive dating agency. In an attempt to broker peace Chyka asks Andrea, Lydia and Gina homewares shopping, which doesn't go to plan. Chyka then hosts an elaborate pooch party for the girls and their fur-children (is it a sign that Janet's small dogs are too scared to leave their Louis Vuitton carrier?). Jackie and Ben show business mentor Chyka the labels on their new cocktail line - while stressing over what else needs doing to get it ready for the big launch. At a glamorous Emirates cocktail party Lydia questions Janet about something Gina divulged in a phone call. Keen to get to the bottom of it, Janet meets Gina for a drink and things quickly turn sour. Will their friendship survive?
If you see "Hector" on the end of a file it means I capped it.
Enjoy, Gaz/Hector :)
